title: Paul Gosar
added: On February 26, 2021, Gosar attended a white nationalist conference<ref name=":0" /> known as "AFPAC" hosted by Holocaust denier [[Nick Fuentes]]. At the event, Fuentes defended the January 6 [[2021 storming of the United States Capitol|storming of the Capitol]] as "awesome" and said that "white people are done being bullied." Gosar attempted to distance himself from the event, saying the next day that he condemns "white racism." <ref>{{Cite web|last=Leber|first=Rebecca|title=GOP congressman skipped the stimulus vote to appear at a white nationalist event|url=https://www.motherjones.com/mojo-wire/2021/02/paul-gosar-nick-fuentes-white-nationalist/|access-date=2021-02-27|website=Mother Jones|language=en-US}}</ref>
